Extra Collections¶

“extra-collections” or “extra” for short is a python package that provides an intuitive python implementation for the most common data structures out there in the world around us. Some of these data structures are simple like “LinkedList”, “Stack” and “Queue” and some of them are much complicated like SkipList, “Trie”, and “RedBlackTree”.

The name was inspired by collections python package that provides a pythonic implementation for the basic data structures. This package provides far more data structures, hence the name “extra-collections”.
